<h2 class="bold font-l">Tower Knight</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The corrupted form of the Knight of the Tower, Alfred, a Knight of the Round Table of Boletaria. He was renowned for his unique Tower Shield, forged to stop almost any physical or magical attack. Once he became a Demon, he grew to a great height and wields a larger form of his shield. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="z6p8sa" data-video-descrip="The last of the gigas, a race that challenged the gods millennia ago." data-video-title="Dione Nephilim" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/z6p8sa_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/0_gob_45.png" data-video-trope="Main/OurGiantsAreBigger" data-video-tropename="Our Giants Are Bigger" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="LightNovel/MonsterGirlDoctor" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/0_gob_45.png">
<p><span class="bold">Dione Nephilim</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="qd7bjv" data-video-descrip="The Last Giant is part of a race of golem-like beings foreign to Drangleic, unlike the deities of Anor Londo found in Dark Souls (characters like Ornstein and Artorias were larger than the Player Character, but still retained human body proportions). Their skin is akin to stone, and they have a hole where their face should be." data-video-title="The Last Giant" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/qd7bjv_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/maxresdefault_025.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/OurGiantsAreBigger" data-video-tropename="Our Giants Are Bigger" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="VideoGame/DarkSouls2,VideoGame/DarkSoulsII" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/maxresdefault_025.jpg">
