<h1 id="overlay-title">Tower Knight</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The corrupted form of the Knight of the Tower, Alfred, a Knight of the Round Table of Boletaria. He was renowned for his unique Tower Shield, forged to stop almost any physical or magical attack. Once he became a Demon, he grew to a great height and wields a larger form of his shield.	</p>
